{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji50.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于“八一”建军节的指示","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于“八一”建军节的指示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年7月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”不能改，这是很重要的一天。我们打响了第一枪，为井冈山的斗争揭开了序幕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个问题是历史问题，历史问题是不容颠倒的。1967年，毛泽东在南京长江摆渡口。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":38,"page_end":38},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}